    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Shoot. Loot. Extract. Will you survive?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SINGLE PLAYER PVE EXTRACTION SHOOTER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy a fully single player extraction shooter experience. Play at your own pace  without the fear of seasons, wipes, or other progression-based resets. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/32e59e8f5d90e7058c0d1c083b20b194.poster.avif?t=1768578126\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/32e59e8f5d90e7058c0d1c083b20b194.webm?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/32e59e8f5d90e7058c0d1c083b20b194.mp4?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GEAR UP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Destroy everything in your path with over 15 armors, 12 backpacks, dozens of guns, and tons of sights, muzzles, silencers, foregrips, magazines, and flashlights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/eda785924b0e51ba5fc5e7723674af9d.poster.avif?t=1768578126\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/eda785924b0e51ba5fc5e7723674af9d.webm?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/eda785924b0e51ba5fc5e7723674af9d.mp4?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >SHOOT AND LOOT</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on various threats as you loot what remains. Hoard over 200 items as you fight off other survivors and the infected.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/86fb15889869e88f0fcf39d76ea6a805.poster.avif?t=1768578126\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/86fb15889869e88f0fcf39d76ea6a805.webm?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/86fb15889869e88f0fcf39d76ea6a805.mp4?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STOCK UP</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bring your spoils back to your stash to use for crafting and base upgrades.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/4c05fd369c8089caec78000a564c1c70.poster.avif?t=1768578126\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/4c05fd369c8089caec78000a564c1c70.webm?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/4c05fd369c8089caec78000a564c1c70.mp4?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >EXTRACT, OR ELSE</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Make it to an extract point before you get taken down by the infected. Be sure to watch out for other survivor's bullets too.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/96d3c5131675f6507bf69f60e0c64a12.poster.avif?t=1768578126\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/96d3c5131675f6507bf69f60e0c64a12.webm?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3321290/extras/96d3c5131675f6507bf69f60e0c64a12.mp4?t=1768578126\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hardcore and Casual Modes - Hardcore mode provides a traditional extraction shooter experience where you lose everything on you if you die before extracting. Looking for something easier? Casual mode offers the excitement of the extraction shooter genre while allowing you to keep the gear you came in with if you die. Say goodbye to &quot;Gear Fear&quot; for good!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No progression wipes or resets. A fully single player extraction shooter experience that you can play at your own pace</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete missions to upgrade traders and collect rewards</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Satisfying Gunplay - Fluid first-person shooting and recoil where your stats actually matter. With over 30 firearms to experiment with, you're sure to find the right one for you</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Gun customization with scopes, grips, tactical devices, muzzles, and magazines</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Stash - Store all the gear and loot you acquire each raid at your base</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Base Progression - Upgrade your base with loot you collect. Expand your stash space, attract new traders, and improve the functions of your base for extra perks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Buying and Trading - Traders have various wares for sale in addition to giving missions. Gear up with what they have to offer or sell your loot to them for extra cash</p></li></ul>",
